name: Liang Wu
summary:
Liang Wu is a 28-year-old Software Engineer living in Los Angeles, California, originally from Beijing, China, and is fluent in English and Mandarin. He studied at the University of Pennsylvania and is now working in the technology industry. Liang describes himself as a man with a hardworking nature who values integrity and creativeness. In his free time, he enjoys coding hackathons, listening to music, and painting. He is open about his liberal political views and his Buddhist religious beliefs. 

Despite being busy, Liang maintains an active lifestyle and occasionally enjoys a drink yet steers clear of smoking or drugs. A straight, Libra, INTJ personality type man, Liang has a preference for monogamous relationships with intentions of finding a long-term partner. He currently has no children but hopes to become a father in the future. His desired partner is a woman aged 23 to 30, who doesn't smoke or drink, leads an active lifestyle, and shares Liang's desire to start a family.
